narrator.desc: This is a white plastic and glass blender. It has a clear glass jar with a white plastic lid. The lid has a black button on it. The base of the blender is white plastic.

scenes: A white blender is placed on a minimalist white kitchen counter against a light gray wall. A gray tea kettle is on the left and a wooden bowl filled with limes is in the background.
The blender is set on a white marble counter. A fruit bowl with bananas, strawberries, and grapes sits next to it. The backdrop is a large window with a view of a city.
The blender is situated on a butcher block counter between a stainless steel sink and a white subway tile backsplash. Above the counter are white floating shelves with plates and bowls.
The blender is beside a bag of flour on a brown wooden table in a commercial kitchen. The background is an industrial-style window with metal frames and exposed brick.
A white blender is sitting on a white and gray marble countertop next to a white ceramic bowl with lemons. In the background are gray cabinets with brass knobs and a white tile backsplash.
